 />\n<br />\n日本校長高島雄平去年年初因為在菲律賓的旅館拍攝一名年僅13到14歲的女童裸照，被當地員警發現他的數位相機中還有超過10張對其他少女進行猥褻的照片，因此菲律賓警方通報日本警察，結果日本員警搜索高島雄平的住所後，竟發現多達400本的裸照相簿，總計有超過14萬張的實體照片，而且高島雄平還一一將不同的對象打上編號，數字超過1萬2千號，年齡從十幾歲的未成年少女到70歲老婦都有。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uk5BLfP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUk5BLfP.png&h=9ec67137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n向上面個架佬致敬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1810670d93df6c5d81eaf22e34570227d7490bbe","tid":975674,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T00:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>這時導遊竟要求她簽免責書，表明若她有甚麼不測，旅行社不負任何責任，「我這時想起香港人在菲律賓搭大巴慘痛的經歷」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣先記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一早都唔應該去D垃圾地方"},{"pid":"7e5bbb632340b2cea744b9c996370365d6526508","tid":975674,"uid":50674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T01:08:07.000Z","msg":"無人睇到重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那人讀中大攞香港護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcd32e2bf96e9347e9e73a55870fdba1d3b0c99","tid":975674,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T01:14:12.000Z","msg":"唱衰完唔好再去,一定砌鳩你"},{"pid":"a536d4e7b2315a0c03929d2a47d27de050769710","tid":975674,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e5bbb632340b2cea744b9c996370365d6526508","tid":975674,"uid":50674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T01:08:07.000Z","msg":"無人睇到重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那人讀中大攞香港護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T01:15:47.000Z","msg":"睇到賓國就無睇內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji